    <title>一次搭站踩坑小记录</title>
    <link href="/Other/%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%90%AD%E7%AB%99%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <url>/Other/%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%90%AD%E7%AB%99%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E5%B0%8F%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo">hexo</h1><p>先看下hexo怎么说：https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</p><p>前提是两个东西：<a href="http://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a> (Node.js版本需不低于 10.13，建议使用 Node.js 12.0 及以上版本)和<ahref="http://git-scm.com/">Git</a></p><p>检查一下，没有问题<imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210142143250.png"alt="image-20221210142143250" /></p><p>然后安装hexo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install -g hexo-cli<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>初始化一个目录，用来存放网站相关的所有文件，我选目录<code>d:\studydocs</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo init d:\studydocs<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> d:\studydocs<br>npm install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210143238569.png"alt="image-20221210143238569" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20221210143238569</figcaption></figure><h1 id="主题">主题</h1><p>然后安装主题tree，https://github.com/wujun234/hexo-theme-tree</p><p>下载主题到 <code>hexo</code> 根目录中 <code>themes</code> 目录下</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/wujun234/hexo-theme-tree.git  themes/tree<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">theme: tree<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看一下效果（在git bash里运行）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo g<span class="hljs-comment"># 生成静态文件</span><br>hexo server<span class="hljs-comment"># 启动本地服务器预览，默认访问地址为http://localhost:4000/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210144548553.png"alt="image-20221210144548553" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20221210144548553</figcaption></figure><hr /><h1 id="小修">小修</h1><p>下面对主题布局进行一些修改</p><p>D:<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">enableComment:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><span class="hljs-comment"># 关掉评论</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">busuanzi:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><span class="hljs-comment"># 关掉访问量统计</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">siteStartYear:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2022</span><span class="hljs-comment"># 底部版权开始年份改为当前2022年</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">searchEngine:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=</span><span class="hljs-comment"># 配置搜索引擎为百度</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">homeHost:</span> <span class="hljs-string">studydocs.cn</span><span class="hljs-comment"># 配置搜索站点名为当前域名</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>D:_partial下找到<code>header.ejs</code>，注释下面的内容，去掉导航栏里UidGeneratror和GitHub图标</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ejs">&lt;li class=&quot;menu-item&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/wujun234/uid-generator-spring-boot-starter&quot; class=&quot;menu-item-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;<br>UidGenerator<br>&lt;/a&gt;<br>&lt;/li&gt;<br>&lt;li class=&quot;menu-item&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/wujun234&quot; class=&quot;menu-item-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-github fa-2x&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;<br>&lt;/a&gt;<br>&lt;/li&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>D:_partial下找到<code>sidebar.ejs</code>，把<code>按回车全站搜索</code>改为更简洁的<code>Search</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ejs">&lt;input id=&quot;search-input&quot; class=&quot;search-input&quot; type=&quot;search&quot; placeholder=&quot;Search&quot;&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>D:<code>favicon.ico</code>，修改一下网站图标</p><p>可以把希望做成图标的图片放到这里转为32*32的图标：https://www.bitbug.net/</p><hr /><p>下面对hexo的配置进行修改</p><p>D:<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">StudyDocs</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">YQ.Geng</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://studydocs.cn</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><p>配置about，参考这里：https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html#new</p><p>about是一个独立页面，使用下面命令创建一个以标题为名字的目录，在目录中放置<code>index.md</code>文件，使用<code>--path</code>参数可以直接完成上面过程</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo new page --path about/index <span class="hljs-string">&quot;About&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210174854178.png"alt="image-20221210174854178" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20221210174854178</figcaption></figure><p>下面就可以在D:<code>index.md</code>进行编辑，即点击About后显示的内容</p><figure><imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210175140041.png"alt="image-20221210175140041" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20221210175140041</figcaption></figure><figure><imgsrc="https://imgbed-1305362743.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/image-20221210175356079.png"alt="image-20221210175356079" /><figcaption aria-hidden="true">image-20221210175356079</figcaption></figure><hr /><h1 id="部署网站">部署网站</h1><p>配置GitHub和本地免密连接，在git bash里进行以下操作</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;raingiving&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;raingiving@gmail.com&quot;</span><br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;raingiving@gmail.com&quot;</span><br>一路回车<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub<br>复制下面的密钥<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在GitHub里，Settings——SSH and GPG keys——New SSHkey——粘贴刚刚的密钥并保存</p><hr /><p>接下来是把博客部署到GitHub，参考：https://bbs.huaweicloud.com/blogs/385834（错字有点多的样子）</p><ol type="1"><li><p>GitHub上建库，仓库名是<code>用户名.github.io</code>，其他全部默认，创建即可</p></li><li><p>安装 <strong>hexo-deployer-git</strong> 插件包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>D:<code>_config.yml</code>，拉到最后Deployment处，修改为</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/RainGiving/raingiving.github.io.git</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>最后部署即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>访问raingiving.github.io即可看到网站已经部署成功</p></li></ol><hr /><p>最后自定义域名</p><p>在GitHub上打开网站所在仓库——Settings——GitHub Pages——Custom domain</p><p>输入自定义域名，点击save，即可（域名第一次输入可能需要去域名注册处做一些配置）</p><hr /><p>其他一些小问题</p><ul><li><p><code>hexo d</code>之后报错： OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection wasreset, errno 10054 解决方法：命令如下，关闭SSL验证</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config --global http.sslVerify <span class="hljs-string">&quot;false&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>hexo d</code>成功上传到GitHub之后，原先设置的Customdomain不见了解决方法：在本地仓库的public目录下新建一个文件<code>CNAME</code>，内容就是自定义域名，这样就不会每次更新仓库内容时把原仓库的这个文件给弄掉了，导致自定义域名失效</p></li></ul><hr /><p>优化以下markdown语法，参考：https://blog.csdn.net/qq_42951560/article/details/123596899</p><h1 id="反复">反复</h1><p>tree主题的代码块样式感觉不佳，但是又没有好的办法解决，于是又启用了文档更详细的<ahref="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">Fluid主题</a></p><p>直接进入博客目录D:，打开GitBash</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install --save hexo-theme-fluid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后创建文件<code>_config.yml</code>，把<ahref="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid/blob/master/_config.yml">_config.yml</a>内容复制进去保存即可</p><p>对Fluid的配置再开一篇记录</p>]]></content>
    
    
